summary: A simple early mod to open a new country to explore and to loot...
descriptionHtml:
As far as I am concerned I have not created much lore on the subject and will be adding soon.
Note this New land mod is in very very early development.
What's in it now.
-East part of the landscape
-Two buildings
-One small Dwemer Ruin
-One NPC
NOTE: There is not much NavMesh follower may not work or be running around weird.

NOTE: I have been working on this for 4 days its not a lot but i plan on working on it for the next year. Thank you

What I plan on doing with the mod. (CAN'T PROMISE)
-Add 20+ hours of side quests and a 7+ hour main quest
-Voice acting to all characters.
-Player home
-More than 15 bandit hide-outs and 6 nordic ruins
-Copper God Temporary summon follower (like spriggons)
-8 citys two villages and several scattered buildings
-Huge mountains.
-Hidden chests make exploring my world worth it.

What might come if I can. (MOST LIKELY NOT TO HAPPEN)
-A quest to travel to main land Atmora. 3+ hours
-A quest to Minmus (using space suits). 10+ hours
-A quest back in time to when Nords still lived on Akatosh. 4+ hours.
-New animals.

NOTE: if this mod goes haywire I will finish putting landscapes and interiors just no quests and custom effect and voice. Just a caution.

Thank you,
William Asquith aka. AsquithGaming

Please Track, endorse, and give feedback.
author: AsquithGaming
